HORN runs in a straight line, smashing everything in its path. It is not bothered even if it rushes headlong into a block of steel. This POK\u00e9MON may feel some pain from the collision the next day, however."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"RHYHORN\u2019s brain is very small. It is so dense, while on a run it forgets why it started running in the first place. It apparently remembers sometimes if it demolishes something."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Once it starts running, it doesn\u2019t stop. Its tiny brain makes it so stupid that it can\u2019t remember why it started running in the first place."},{"version":"firered","text":"Strong, but not too bright, this POK\u00e9MON can shatter even a skyscraper with its charging TACKLES."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Its massive bones are 1,000 times harder than human bones. Its TACKLE can knock a semitrailer flying."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its body is clad in a thick hide, and its tackles topple buildings. Unfortunately, it is not smart."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its body is clad in a thick hide, and its tackles topple buildings. Unfortunately, it is not smart."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its powerful tackles can destroy anything. However, it is too slow witted to help people work."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"It is inept at turning because of its four short legs. It can only charge and run in one direction."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It doesn\u2019t care if there is anything in its way. It just charges and destroys all obstacles."},{"version":"black","text":"Its powerful tackles can destroy anything. However, it is too slow witted to help people work."},{"version":"white","text":"Its powerful tackles can destroy anything. However, it is too slow witted to help people work."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its powerful tackles can destroy anything. However, it is too slow witted to help people work."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its powerful tackles can destroy anything. However, it is too slow witted to help people work."},{"version":"x","text":"Strong, but not too bright, this Pok\u00e9mon can shatter even a skyscraper with its charging Tackles."},{"version":"y","text":"It is inept at turning because of its four short legs. It can only charge and run in one direction."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Rhyhorn runs in a straight line, smashing everything in its path. It is not bothered even if it rushes headlong into a block of steel. This Pok\u00e9mon may feel some pain from the collision the next day, however."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Rhyhorn\u2019s brain is very small. It is so dense, while on a run it forgets why it started running in the first place. It apparently remembers sometimes if it demolishes something."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"A Pok\u00e9mon with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won\u2019t stop running until it falls asleep."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"A Pok\u00e9mon with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won\u2019t stop running until it falls asleep."},{"version":"sword","text":"Strong, but not too bright, this Pok\u00e9mon can shatter even a skyscraper with its charging tackles."},{"version":"shield","text":"It can remember only one thing at a time. Once it starts rushing, it forgets why it started."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Ludicrously strong\u2014when it butts heads with a mountain, it is the mountain that shatters. But its short legs struggle with turns, and it is incapable of stopping unless it collides with something."}],"evo":{"name":"rhyhorn","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"rhydon","level":1,"min_level":42,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":n